entries.journal_entry_description: Fiask Nidori is looking to make a new dish. He wants you to kill rats for their meat on Station Gamma, to use as his secret ingredient.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Kill a rat in Station Gamma for a sample of meat.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Kill a rat in Station Gamma
entries.task01_comm_message_text: It's edible right? Good, get me five more.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: It has been determined that the meat is edible. You are to recover five more samples.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return with the meat you collected to Fiask Nidori
